     *
     * FLIP_H: Image bottom trimmed before transform<p>
     * FLIP_V: Image right trimmed before transform<p>
     * TRANSPOSE: No trimming required before transform<p>
     * TRANSVERSE: Image right and bottom trimmed before transform<p>
